metadata.name: ENGAGE 1
metadata.description: The ENGAGE collection is based on two driving concepts. First, our pure passion for art. Second, the thousands of screen prints we've created over the last 20 years. Our genesis collection of 100 1/1 pieces combines random layers of test-printed posters that were hand-pulled at our studio in Newport, KY. The stencil cut image overlay was prominent in our early work and shows "Claire" looking over her shoulder at the viewer, drawing them in. Each piece is a digitally crafted collage of color and imagery from iconic bands, shows and more - all with their own story.
